sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant UI
    participant API
    participant Engine
    participant Redis
    participant PostgreSQL

    User->>UI: Open dashboard
    UI->>API: GET /api/*
    API->>Redis: lookup context
    Redis-->>API: cached data (optional)
    API->>Engine: evaluate tool call
    Engine->>Redis: cache decision
    Engine-->>API: allow/deny + reason
    API->>PostgreSQL: store audit event
    API-->>UI: decision payload
    UI-->>User: render result
